‘If I can medal at all four major championships, that would be a great achievement.

‘I’d love to win a gold at the World Championships next year to add to my European gold - and then I’d like to try and medal at the Olympics in Rio. Then another target is to break the British Record. But it’s all going to take a lot of hard work.’

